txt.en: From among the ranks of the Wargs who infest the walls of Azanulbizar champions are chosen to bear the enemy's most elite warriors.
'You have put a sizeable dent in the Warg population, my friend. The enemy will have to walk on their own two feet to the battlefield now, hah hah!'

'The mountain passes and hillsides are filled with deadly Wargs. Their burrows wind deep under hill and mountain, where they breed faster than Men. From among their ranks, the deadliest and strongest are chosen to bear the enemy into battle. We must do what we can to thin their ranks before the enemy gains these allies.'
